{"tid":1427761,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"探討 「光復香港 時代革命」與 「五大訴求」既關係","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:48:33.000Z","uid":10524,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"33746d321dd06cad7d963bf1a36d20aec95bea46","tid":1427761,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"經過文宣group 內激烈討論<br />\n<br />\n總結出兩者其實可以講成 願景和實際目標既分別<br />\n<br />\n所以大家要做既係等更多人明白，而唔係撤回呢一個大家都喜愛既口號<br />\n<br />\n其實五大訴求可以完全體現係呢八個字入面<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港」 可以意指 恢復香港嘅核心價值 <br />\n<br />\n1-徹回惡法 代表著尊重基本法 港人治港 高度自治<br />\n2-收回暴動定義 代表著尊重集會及言論自由<br />\n3-釋放被捕義士 代表著捍衛執法司法公義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「時代革命」 可以意指 革新政制和思想要追上「時代」的步伐<br />\n<br />\n4-成立獨立調查委員會，革新監警機關及公權力<br />\n5-實行真雙普選，賦予香港真正民主社會 ，屨行基本法及中英聯合聲明中對香港人既承諾<br />\n<br />\n除左拆彈之外 都希望大家一齊反思一下 <br />\n呢句口號對大家既意義"},{"pid":"e325952b7d8acc06d64610485e78a42352995991","tid":1427761,"uid":10524,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得除左懷念天琦之外 <br />\n仲因為正正反影現況"},{"pid":"b74f1193bcf6cade0a8fbb6cec1ac9336a81d12a","tid":1427761,"uid":10524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"不如當收集意見<br />\n<br />\n大家填一下<br />\n<br />\n我係______，對我黎講<br />\n光復香港係_________<br />\n時代革命係_________<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以比我做文宣素材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b2a1d9cc07db63a132b5b39d0050aca67bda75","tid":1427761,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d3757eabbc5263fc27070c382ffb894fbf85c92","tid":1427761,"uid":59989,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tri2rCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTri2rCG.jpg&h=42b73c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tet9Q4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTet9Q4m.jpg&h=624b9fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bh1vAv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbh1vAv2.png&h=bd529e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc82d3c07b235127fb82da94dfb9c79f744ff0c2","tid":1427761,"uid":10524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"比個例子大家<br />\n<br />\n我  係 設計師<br />\n光復香港 係 香港啲設計又有特色又多人欣賞<br />\n時代革命 係 D無料老屎忽唔好再浪費D job"},{"pid":"22bedcc31faf1e4e465140f5bea0950dfc98e47b","tid":1427761,"uid":10524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d3757eabbc5263fc27070c382ffb894fbf85c92","tid":1427761,"uid":59989,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tri2rCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTri2rCG.jpg&h=42b73c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tet9Q4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTet9Q4m.jpg&h=624b9fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bh1vAv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbh1vAv2.png&h=bd529e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"Hey"},{"pid":"aec66dd5da5f6c71c2188c1b8c5efeb7ccb0adce","tid":1427761,"uid":287033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"話說我夢遊的時候，整左個Wikimedia Server (你當佢係普通維基百科).<br />\n<br />\n其實我見好似無一個地方去整合過去幾個月的資料。但係小弟文筆唔好，墨水唔多滴，就想睇下各路英雄有無興趣去一齊寫。<br />\n<br />\n進度: 只起好server , 未有內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://HongKongProtest.rf.gf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHongKongProtest.rf.gf&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Zw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=4547aac3\" da